Your vision, now in production

Android Studio Panda 2 is here. Go from concept to working app faster with
new agentic experiences designed to handle the heavy lifting for you.

Go from idea to app

With the New Project flow, you can describe your vision in natural language
or even upload a UI mockup and let Gemini (or your LLM of choice via API
key) build the foundation for you instead of spending hours wiring up
dependencies.

How it works:

1. Open the New Project Wizard and select "Create with AI".

2. Describe your app's flow (e.g., "A workout tracker with a calendar view
and local storage"). You can even upload images for style inspiration.

3. The agent creates a project plan, writes the Kotlin and Compose code,
resolves build errors autonomously, and deploys a working draft to your
emulator.

Upgrade to Build with AI at https://developer.android.com/studio

